    <item>
      <title>由于以色列和哈马斯的反击，拜登结束加沙战争的努力受挫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/hamas-rejects-gaza-peace-plan-without-permanent-cease-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯跟随以色列，拒绝接受总统乔·拜登结束加沙战争的努力，双方都表示，必须满足各自提出的永久停火条件，他们才会同意停战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/hamas-rejects-gaza-peace-plan-without-permanent-cease-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 16:56:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>律师称亨特·拜登并未“故意”撒谎购买枪支</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/hunter-biden-didn-t-knowingly-lie-to-buy-gun-his-lawyer-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亨特·拜登的律师周二在特拉华州联邦法院对他的审判中告诉陪审团，亨特·拜登在 2018 年填写购枪表格并勾选了声称自己没有吸毒的方框时并没有故意撒谎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/hunter-biden-didn-t-knowingly-lie-to-buy-gun-his-lawyer-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 16:12:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安迪·金赢得新泽西州民主党参议院初选；共和党的蒂姆·希伊赢得蒙大拿州初选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-04/after-guilty-verdict-trump-will-appear-on-the-ballot-in-the-last-presidential-primaries-of-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约（美联社）——总统乔·拜登和前总统唐纳德·特朗普周二在几个州赢得了民主党和共和党初选，这是 2024 年初选日程中最后几场竞选之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-04/after-guilty-verdict-trump-will-appear-on-the-ballot-in-the-last-presidential-primaries-of-2024</guid>
